This document lists the hardware and connection used for creating and testing this project.

Harware
RobotDyn Nano V3 arduino clone
RobotDyn Light Dimmer Module
HC-05 bluetooth module
DS3231 RTC module
Push button


Connections

Arduino - Light Dimmer
5V - VCC
GND - GND
Pin 3 (interupt pin 1) - ZC
Pin A2 - PWM

Arduino - HC-05
Pin 5 - 1K resistor - RXD 
	RXD then also connects to GND by a 2K resistor
Pin 4 - TXD
GND - GND
5V - VCC

Arduino - RTC
A5 (Nano's SCL pin)  - SCL
A4 (Nano's SDA pin) - SDA
GND - GND
5V - Vin

Arduino - Push Button
Pin 2 (interrupt 0) - top left button pin
GND - 10K resistor - top right button pin
5V - bottom right button pin